description:
Lainey Wilson stops by the studio to talk about her recent No. 1s, her career skyrocketing and the fan who got her face tattooed on her body. Bobby talks about a Harry Styles superfan who freaked out when she met him. We share what celebs would give us a similar reaction. Caller Will in Texas calls in to challenge Lunchbox on something.
